data.description: Beautiful New Construction, One of a kind! This 3 bedroom, plus office; 2 bathroom Home is in an Excellent location of Lee Acres. Minutes from shopping and restaurants. Some of the top of the line features are: granite counter tops, island in the kitchen, tile throughout, stainless steal appliances, soft close wood cabinets, and all impact glass doors and windows. Open Lanai and two car garage, it has everything you could ask for! Come see it before it's gone!
